msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:69"
msgid "Returns: `boolean`."
msgstr "返回：`boolean`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:71
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:71"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:73
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:73"
msgid ""
"`nil` and `false` are treated as falsy. All other Lua values are treated as "
"truthy."
msgstr "`nil` 和 `false` 会被视为 falsy，其他所有 Lua 值都会被视为 truthy。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:75
msgid "Iteration stops as soon as a truthy result is found."
msgstr "一旦找到 truthy 结果，遍历就会停止。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:76
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:76"
msgid "Empty lists return `false`."
msgstr "空表会返回 `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:86
msgid "ptool.tbl.all"
msgstr "ptool.tbl.all"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:88
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:88"
