msgid ""
"`ptool.tbl.all(list, fn)` returns `true` only when the callback produces a "
"truthy result for every item."
msgstr "`ptool.tbl.all(list, fn)` 只有在回调对每一项都返回 truthy 结果时才会返回 "
"`true`。"

