msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:202
msgid "The list is scanned from left to right."
msgstr "列表会从左到右扫描。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:203
msgid "Equality uses normal Lua `==` semantics."
msgstr "比较使用标准的 Lua `==` 语义。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:204
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:204"
msgid "Empty lists return `false`."
msgstr "空表会返回 `false`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:212
msgid "ptool.tbl.reduce"
msgstr "ptool.tbl.reduce"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:214
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:214"
msgid "`v0.10.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.10.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:216
msgid "`ptool.tbl.reduce(list, initial, fn)` folds a list into a single value."
msgstr "`ptool.tbl.reduce(list, initial, fn)` 会把一个列表折叠成单个值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:218
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:218"
msgid "`list` (table, required): A dense list table."
msgstr "`list`（table，必填）：一个致密的顺序表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:219
msgid "`initial` (any, required): The explicit initial accumulator value."
msgstr "`initial`（any，必填）：显式提供的初始累加器值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:220
msgid ""
"`fn` (function, required): A callback that receives `(acc, value, index)` "
"and must return a non-`nil` value."
msgstr "`fn`（function，必填）：回调函数，接收 `(acc, value, index)`，并且必须返回非 "
"`nil` 的值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:222
msgid "Returns: `any`."
msgstr "返回：`any`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:224
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:224"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:226
msgid "`initial` is always required, even for non-empty lists."
msgstr "即使列表非空，也必须始终显式传入 `initial`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:227
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:227"
msgid "`fn` is called once for each item in order."
msgstr "`fn` 会按顺序对每一项调用一次。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:228
msgid "Each callback result becomes the next accumulator value."
msgstr "每次回调的返回值都会成为下一次的累加器值。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:229
msgid ""
"If `fn` returns `nil`, the call raises an error instead of losing the "
"accumulator state."
msgstr "如果 `fn` 返回 `nil`，调用会直接报错，而不是丢失累加器状态。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:231
msgid "Empty lists return `initial` unchanged."
msgstr "空表会原样返回 `initial`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:241
msgid "ptool.tbl.flat_map"
msgstr "ptool.tbl.flat_map"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:243
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:243"
msgid "`v0.10.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.10.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:245
msgid ""
"`ptool.tbl.flat_map(list, fn)` maps each item to a dense list table and then "
"concatenates those returned lists into one new dense list."
msgstr ""
"`ptool.tbl.flat_map(list, fn)` 会把每一项映射为一个致密顺序表，再把这些返回的"
"顺序表按顺序拼接成一个新的致密顺序表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:248
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:248"
msgid "`list` (table, required): A dense list table."
msgstr "`list`（table，必填）：一个致密的顺序表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:249
msgid ""
"`fn` (function, required): A callback that receives `(value, index)` and "
"must return a dense list table."
msgstr "`fn`（function，必填）：回调函数，接收 `(value, index)`，并且必须返回一个致密"
"顺序表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:251
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:251"
msgid "Returns: `table`."
msgstr "返回：`table`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:253
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:253"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:255
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:255"
msgid "`fn` is called once for each item in order."
msgstr "`fn` 会按顺序对每一项调用一次。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:256
msgid "Each callback result must be a dense list table."
msgstr "每次回调的返回值都必须是致密顺序表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:257
msgid "Returning a non-table or a non-dense list raises an error."
msgstr "如果返回的不是表，或者返回的是非致密列表，就会报错。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:258
msgid "Empty lists return an empty list."
msgstr "空表会返回空列表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:268
msgid "ptool.tbl.concat"
msgstr "ptool.tbl.concat"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:270
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:270"
msgid "`v0.6.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.6.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:272
msgid ""
"`ptool.tbl.concat(...)` concatenates one or more dense list tables into a "
"new list."
msgstr "`ptool.tbl.concat(...)` 将一个或多个致密顺序表按顺序拼接成新的顺序表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:275
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:275"
msgid "`...` (table, required): One or more dense list tables."
msgstr "`...`（table，必填）：一个或多个致密顺序表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:276
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:276"
msgid "Returns: `table`."
msgstr "返回：`table`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:278
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:278"
msgid "Behavior:"
msgstr "行为说明："

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:280
msgid "Arguments are appended from left to right."
msgstr "参数会从左到右依次追加。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:281
msgid "Empty lists are allowed."
msgstr "允许传入空表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:282
msgid "The input tables are not modified."
msgstr "输入表不会被修改。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:290
msgid "ptool.tbl.join"
msgstr "ptool.tbl.join"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:292
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:292"
msgid "`v0.6.0` - Introduced."
msgstr "`v0.6.0` - 引入。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:294
msgid "`ptool.tbl.join(...)` is an alias of `ptool.tbl.concat(...)`."
msgstr "`ptool.tbl.join(...)` 是 `ptool.tbl.concat(...)` 的别名。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:296
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:296"
msgid "`...` (table, required): One or more dense list tables."
msgstr "`...`（table，必填）：一个或多个致密顺序表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:297
msgctxt "/Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:297"
msgid "Returns: `table`."
msgstr "返回：`table`。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:305
msgid "List Rules"
msgstr "顺序表规则"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:307
msgid "`ptool.tbl` currently supports only dense list tables."
msgstr "`ptool.tbl` 当前只支持致密顺序表。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:309
msgid "Keys must be integers."
msgstr "键必须是整数。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:310
msgid "Keys must start at `1`."
msgstr "键必须从 `1` 开始。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:311
msgid "Keys must be contiguous without gaps."
msgstr "键必须连续，不能有空洞。"

#: /Users/peterlits/Proj/PeterlitsZo/ptool/website/docs/lua-api/tbl.md:312
msgid "Sparse tables and dictionary-style tables raise errors."
msgstr "稀疏表和字典风格的表都会抛错。"

